      • acceptsIncomplete

        public java.lang.Boolean acceptsIncomplete()
        Gets the acceptsIncomplete. A value of true indicates that both the IBM Cloud platform and the requesting client support asynchronous deprovisioning. If this parameter is not included in the request, and the broker can only deprovision a service instance of the requested plan asynchronously, the broker MUST reject the request with a `422` Unprocessable Entity.
        Returns:
        the acceptsIncomplete
